\v 13 \w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5020"\w* became very angry. \w He|strong="H5020"\w* commanded \add his soldiers\add* \w to|strong="H6925"\w* bring \w in|strong="H4430"\w* \w Shadrach|strong="H7715"\w*, \w Meshach|strong="H4336"\w*, \w and|strong="H4336"\w* Abednego. When they \w were|strong="H1400"\w* brought \w to|strong="H6925"\w* \w him|strong="H6925"\w*,  
\v 14 \w Nebuchadnezzar|strong="H5020"\w* \w said|strong="H6032"\w* \w to|strong="H6966"\w* them, “\w Is|strong="H1768"\w* it \w true|strong="H6656"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w you|strong="H1768"\w* three men \w have|strong="H5020"\w* refused \w to|strong="H6966"\w* \w worship|strong="H5457"\w* \w my|strong="H1768"\w* gods \w or|strong="H3809"\w* \w the|strong="H5020"\w* \w gold|strong="H1722"\w* \w statue|strong="H6755"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w I|strong="H1768"\w* \w have|strong="H5020"\w* \w set|strong="H6966"\w* \w up|strong="H6966"\w*?  
