\s1 The explanation of the vision  
\p
\v 15 As for me, \w Daniel|strong="H1841"\w*, I \w was|strong="H1841"\w* very terrified \w by|strong="H2376"\w* what I had seen \w in|strong="H1841"\w* that \w vision|strong="H2376"\w*, \w and|strong="H1841"\w* I did not know what \w to|strong="H1841"\w* think about it.  
