\p
\v 17  \add He said\add*, “\w The|strong="H4481"\w* four huge \w beasts|strong="H2423"\w* represent four kingdoms/empires \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w will|strong="H1768"\w* exist on \w the|strong="H4481"\w* earth.  
