\v 22 \w But|strong="H1768"\w* \w then|strong="H1768"\w* \w the|strong="H1768"\w* Supreme God, \w the|strong="H1768"\w* \w one|strong="H6922"\w* \w who|strong="H1768"\w* \w had|strong="H1768"\w* been living forever, \w came|strong="H4291"\w* \w and|strong="H4437"\w* judged \w in|strong="H4437"\w* favor \w of|strong="H4437"\w* \w the|strong="H1768"\w* people \w who|strong="H1768"\w* belonged \w to|strong="H5705"\w* \w him|strong="H3052"\w*. \w And|strong="H4437"\w* \add I knew that\add* it \w was|strong="H1780"\w* \w time|strong="H2166"\w* \w for|strong="H5705"\w* God’s people \w to|strong="H5705"\w* receive authority \add to rule\add*.   
\p
\v 23  \add Then\add* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* man \w who|strong="H1768"\w* \w was|strong="H1934"\w* standing \w there|strong="H1768"\w* said \add to me\add*, “\w The|strong="H3606"\w* \w fourth|strong="H7244"\w* \w beast|strong="H2423"\w* represents \w an|strong="H4437"\w* empire \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w will|strong="H1768"\w* exist on \w the|strong="H3606"\w* earth; \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \add empire\add* \w will|strong="H1768"\w* \w be|strong="H1934"\w* \w different|strong="H8133"\w* \w from|strong="H4481"\w* \w all|strong="H3606"\w* \add other\add* empires. \add The army of\add* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* empire \w will|strong="H1768"\w* \w crush|strong="H1855"\w*/kill \add people all over\add* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* world \w and|strong="H1855"\w* trample \add on their bodies\add*.  
\v 24 \w As|strong="H4437"\w* \w for|strong="H4481"\w* \w its|strong="H4481"\w* \w ten|strong="H6236"\w* \w horns|strong="H7162"\w*, they represent \w ten|strong="H6236"\w* \w kings|strong="H4430"\w* who \w will|strong="H1932"\w* rule \w that|strong="H7162"\w* empire, \add one after the other\add*. \w Then|strong="H4430"\w* another \add king\add* \w will|strong="H1932"\w* appear. \w He|strong="H1932"\w* \w will|strong="H1932"\w* be \w different|strong="H8133"\w* \w from|strong="H4481"\w* \w the|strong="H4481"\w* \w previous|strong="H6933"\w* \w kings|strong="H4430"\w*. \w He|strong="H1932"\w* \w will|strong="H1932"\w* defeat \w the|strong="H4481"\w* \w three|strong="H8532"\w* \w kings|strong="H4430"\w* \add that were represented by the three horns that were pulled out\add*.  
\v 25 \w He|strong="H5705"\w* \w will|strong="H5732"\w* revile \w the|strong="H5705"\w* Supreme God, \w and|strong="H2166"\w* \w he|strong="H5705"\w* \w will|strong="H5732"\w* oppress God’s people. \w He|strong="H5705"\w* \w will|strong="H5732"\w* try \w to|strong="H5705"\w* \w change|strong="H8133"\w* \w the|strong="H5705"\w* \add sacred\add* festivals \w and|strong="H2166"\w* \w their|strong="H3052"\w* \add religious\add* \w laws|strong="H1882"\w*/regulations. \w He|strong="H5705"\w* \w will|strong="H5732"\w* control \w them|strong="H3052"\w* \w for|strong="H5705"\w* three \w and|strong="H2166"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w half|strong="H6387"\w* years.   
\p
\v 26 But there \w will|strong="H7985"\w* \w be|strong="H1780"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* session/meeting \w of|strong="H5491"\w* \w the|strong="H5705"\w* \w court|strong="H1780"\w*/judges \w in|strong="H3488"\w* heaven, \w and|strong="H5705"\w* that king’s \w authority|strong="H7985"\w*/power \w will|strong="H7985"\w* \w be|strong="H1780"\w* \w taken|strong="H5709"\w* \w away|strong="H5709"\w*, \w and|strong="H5705"\w* \w he|strong="H5705"\w* \w will|strong="H7985"\w* \w be|strong="H1780"\w* completely \w destroyed|strong="H8046"\w*.  
\v 27 \w Then|strong="H1768"\w* \w all|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* power \w and|strong="H8065"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* \w greatness|strong="H7238"\w* \w of|strong="H4437"\w* \w all|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* \w kingdoms|strong="H4437"\w* on \w the|strong="H3606"\w* earth \w will|strong="H1768"\w* \w be|strong="H5957"\w* \w given|strong="H3052"\w* \w to|strong="H3052"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* \w people|strong="H5972"\w* \w who|strong="H1768"\w* belong \w to|strong="H3052"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* Supreme God. \w The|strong="H3606"\w* \w kingdom|strong="H4437"\w* \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w he|strong="H1768"\w* rules (\w OR|strong="H3068"\w*, \w they|strong="H1768"\w* rule) \w will|strong="H1768"\w* endure \w forever|strong="H5957"\w*. \w And|strong="H8065"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* rulers \w of|strong="H4437"\w* \w all|strong="H3606"\w* \w the|strong="H3606"\w* nations on \w the|strong="H3606"\w* earth \w will|strong="H1768"\w* \w serve|strong="H6399"\w* \w and|strong="H8065"\w* \w obey|strong="H8086"\w* \w him|strong="H3052"\w* (\w OR|strong="H3068"\w*, \w them|strong="H3052"\w*).”   
\p
\v 28 \w That|strong="H1768"\w* \w is|strong="H1768"\w* \add what I saw in\add* \w my|strong="H5922"\w* vision/dream. \w I|strong="H1768"\w*, \w Daniel|strong="H1841"\w*, \w was|strong="H1841"\w* terrified, \w with|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* result \w that|strong="H1768"\w* \w my|strong="H5922"\w* \w face|strong="H2122"\w* became \w pale|strong="H8133"\w*. \w But|strong="H1768"\w* \w I|strong="H1768"\w* did not tell anyone \w about|strong="H5922"\w* \w the|strong="H5922"\w* vision \add that I had seen\add*.   
\c 8  
\s1 Daniel’s vision of a ram and a goat  
\p
\v 1 During \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w third|strong="H7969"\w* \w year|strong="H8141"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w Belshazzar|strong="H1112"\w* \w was|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* \add of Babylonia\add*, \w I|strong="H7200"\w* \w had|strong="H4428"\w* \w another|strong="H7200"\w* \w vision|strong="H2377"\w*.  
\v 2 \w In|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w vision|strong="H2377"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w Susa|strong="H7800"\w*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* capital city \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w Elam|strong="H5867"\w* \w Province|strong="H4082"\w*. \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \add standing\add* \w alongside|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Ulai Canal.  
