\v 4 \w The|strong="H3605"\w* ram butted/knocked \w away|strong="H5337"\w* \add with its horns\add* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w was|strong="H3027"\w* \w west|strong="H3220"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w was|strong="H3027"\w* \w north|strong="H6828"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w was|strong="H3027"\w* \w south|strong="H5045"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w it|strong="H6213"\w*. \w There|strong="H5975"\w* \w were|strong="H3027"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* \add other\add* \w animals|strong="H2416"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w were|strong="H3027"\w* \w able|strong="H3027"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w oppose|strong="H5975"\w* \w it|strong="H6213"\w*, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w none|strong="H3808"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w could|strong="H5337"\w* \w rescue|strong="H5337"\w*/\w save|strong="H5337"\w* \add other animals\add* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w its|strong="H3605"\w* \w power|strong="H3027"\w*. \w The|strong="H3605"\w* ram \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w whatever|strong="H3605"\w* \w it|strong="H6213"\w* wanted \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w became|strong="H1431"\w* \w very|strong="H6213"\w* powerful.   
\p
\v 5 \w While|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* thinking \add about what I had seen, in the vision\add* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w saw|strong="H2009"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w goat|strong="H5795"\w* \w come|strong="H1961"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w west|strong="H4628"\w*. \w It|strong="H5921"\w* \w ran|strong="H1961"\w* \w across|strong="H4480"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w land|strong="H6440"\w* \w so|strong="H4480"\w* quickly, \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \add it seemed like\add* \w its|strong="H3605"\w* feet \w did|strong="H5869"\w* \w not|strong="H1961"\w* \w touch|strong="H5060"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w ground|strong="H6440"\w*. \w This|strong="H6440"\w* \w goat|strong="H5795"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w one|strong="H3605"\w* very large \w horn|strong="H7161"\w* \w between|strong="H5921"\w* \w its|strong="H3605"\w* \w eyes|strong="H5869"\w*.  
