\s1 Gabriel explained the vision  
\p
\v 15 \w While|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w*, \w Daniel|strong="H1840"\w*, \w was|strong="H1961"\w* trying \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w understand|strong="H7200"\w* \w what|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w vision|strong="H2377"\w* meant, \w suddenly|strong="H2009"\w* \add an angel\add* \w who|strong="H1397"\w* resembled \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H1397"\w* \w stood|strong="H5975"\w*/\w appeared|strong="H7200"\w* \w in|strong="H5975"\w* \w front|strong="H5048"\w* \w of|strong="H4758"\w* \w me|strong="H7200"\w*.  
