\p
\v 20-21 Then he said, “◄Do you know why I came to you?/I will tell you why I came to you.► [RHQ] It is to reveal to you what is written in the book which reveals/contains God’s truth. But now I must return to fight against \add the evil spirit\add* who rules the kingdom of Persia. After I have defeated him, \add the evil angel\add* who guards Greece will appear \add and I must defeat him\add*. Michael, who guards you \add Israeli people\add*, will help me, but there is no one else to help me.”   
\c 11  
\nb
\v 1 “\w As|strong="H8141"\w* \w for|strong="H5975"\w* \w me|strong="H2388"\w*, during \w the|strong="H2388"\w* first \w year|strong="H8141"\w* \w that|strong="H8141"\w* \w Darius|strong="H1867"\w* \w was|strong="H8141"\w* king, \w I|strong="H8141"\w* \w helped|strong="H2388"\w* \w and|strong="H2388"\w* \w encouraged|strong="H2388"\w* Michael.”   
\s1 The message about the kings of Egypt and Syria  
\p
\v 2  \add The angel also said\add*, “\w And|strong="H4428"\w* what \w I|strong="H2009"\w* am going \w to|strong="H4428"\w* \w reveal|strong="H5782"\w* \w to|strong="H4428"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w now|strong="H6258"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* truly \add happen\add*. \w There|strong="H2009"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w be|strong="H5750"\w* \w three|strong="H7969"\w* \w more|strong="H5750"\w* \w kings|strong="H4428"\w* \w to|strong="H4428"\w* \w rule|strong="H4438"\w* \w Persia|strong="H6539"\w*, \add one after the other\add*. \w Then|strong="H2009"\w* \w there|strong="H2009"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w be|strong="H5750"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w fourth|strong="H7243"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*, \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w be|strong="H5750"\w* \w much|strong="H1419"\w* \w richer|strong="H6238"\w* \w than|strong="H1419"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* others. \w As|strong="H3605"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* result \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \add his giving\add* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H4428"\w* money \add to people, they will enable him to\add* \w become|strong="H6238"\w* \w very|strong="H1419"\w* powerful. \w Then|strong="H2009"\w* \w he|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* incite/persuade \w many|strong="H1419"\w* nations [HYP] \add to fight\add* \w against|strong="H5782"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w kingdom|strong="H4438"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w Greece|strong="H3120"\w*.   
\p
\v 3 \w Then|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H7227"\w* \w powerful|strong="H1368"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* appear \add in Greece\add*. \w He|strong="H6213"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w rule|strong="H4910"\w* \w over|strong="H4428"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H7227"\w* \w large|strong="H7227"\w* empire, \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w he|strong="H6213"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* whatever \w he|strong="H6213"\w* wants \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w*.  
